ign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> BG&lt; other fear Golems</span><hr size=1> The BG is a push over if you have the healing power for any other fear golem you very able to do the BG.  The way I have always done the BG from a wizards stand point is pre 60 use fire and cold lures.  Do not even to both start nuking before 60 as you will go OOM fast as it is a decently long fight based on what you say you have for a raid force abut 10 mins.  However the new resists may have changed what spells can be used.  I would suggest trying droughts and rains just to see near the beginning of the fight.<br>
